data.description: Located in the prestigious Crooked Creek community in Milton, Georgia, renowned for its exceptional golf, swim, and tennis facilities, this beautiful home is an outstanding find for discerning buyers. The residence features six bedrooms and five bathrooms spread across a spacious layout that includes a fully-equipped in-law suite on the terrace level, complete with its own kitchen, bedroom, bathroom, and family room. This makes it perfect for extended family living or hosting guests with comfort and privacy.    The property is situated on a large, private wooded and fenced lot, offering an ideal setting for both relaxation and entertaining. The home is bathed in beautiful natural sunlight and has been updated throughout. Recent enhancements include all-new paint, updated lighting fixtures, and refinished hardwood floors that add warmth and charm to the space.    The large kitchen is a chef’s delight, adjacent to a cozy breakfast sunroom that overlooks the serene outdoor scenery. A fireside great room serves as the heart of the home, providing a spacious yet inviting area for gatherings. Additionally, there is a guest bedroom on the main level, adding convenience and accessibility.    Crooked Creek residents enjoy access to an array of top-tier amenities. These include two swimming pools, a thrilling 140 ft water slide, a zero-entry kids' pool with water spray features, 10 lighted tennis courts, and 4 pickleball courts. The community also offers a full-time tennis staff, a competitive swim team, a playground, a basketball court, and a community clubhouse complete with meeting rooms, a catering kitchen, and a bar.    The home’s location is especially advantageous, situated close to the best public and private schools in Milton, and just minutes from Halycon, Avalon, Downtown Alpharetta, and GA 400, making it perfect for families and professionals alike. This residence offers the perfect blend of luxury, convenience, and access to community facilities, making it an ideal choice for a high-quality lifestyle.
